branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VX3 series is a direct operated, 3 port solenoid valve, for use with a wide variety of fluids. It has an enclosure equivalent to IP65 and with its special construction, metal noise is reduced (DC specification). Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.08 to 0.38.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Max. system pressure: water, air, oil 2.0 MPa; steam 1.0 MPa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduced power consumption: 4.5W (size 1), 7W (size 2), 10.5W (size 3)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Port size: 1/8 to 3/8 inch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IP65 enclosure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UL94V-0 conformed flame resistant mold coil material&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

